trans-unit.target: TEXT_REGROC2JAQUOINIE_00671_JAQUOINIE_000_000<tab>I am a soldier in the service of Lord Aurvael de Haillenarte. If you seek my master, I am afraid he is occupied with preparations for a new undertaking.
TEXT_REGROC2JAQUOINIE_00671_JAQUOINIE_000_001<tab>I am a soldier in the service of Lord Aurvael de Haillenarte. If you seek my master, he is presently in the Firmament for a new undertaking.
TEXT_REGROC2JAQUOINIE_00671_JAQUOINIE_000_002<tab>However, I should be pleased to assist you with any lockboxes you may possess, as well as trade with you for your sky pirate spoils.
TEXT_REGROC2JAQUOINIE_00671_JAQUOINIE_000_003<tab>Owing to recent developments, these items are not as common as they once were, but should you chance to acquire them, please feel free to come to me.
TEXT_REGROC2JAQUOINIE_00671_JAQUOINIE_000_010<tab>If you seek my lord Aurvael, I am afraid he is occupied with preparations for a new undertaking.
